The paper proposes a method for modeling human movement, which involves learning decision models and integrating system dynamics. This suggests that the paper could fall under several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) for the learning aspect, Machine Learning (cs.LG) for the decision model, and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) for the human movement aspect. Additionally, the paper involves modeling physical systems, which could fall under Systems and Control (cs.SY), and the applications of the research could relate to Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC).
